{"tid":1001884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓SK海力士發17倍月薪獎金 員工竟嫌少","createTime":"2019-01-30T13:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T16:53:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7c0c724df3b45cce70440d99daa422fb99b54e","tid":1001884,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/01/30/phpnfkTl8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2FphpnfkTl8.jpg&h=a9d7cd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓SK海力士上週決定向員工發放等同於月薪17倍的特別獎金，然而員工拒絕獎金並要求公司加碼，遭批「太貪心」。（路透檔案照）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕南韓《韓國時報》報導， 南韓記憶體大廠SK海力士由於2018年公司創下佳績，上週決定向員工發放相當於基本月薪17倍的特別獎金，然而生產線員工拒絕獎金並要求公司加碼，遭批「太貪心」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSK海力士生產線員工工會週一開會投票，否決了工會領袖和管理階層提出的臨時薪資協議，並表達對獎金的不滿，SK海力士與產線員工的薪資談判回到原點，獎金的發放時間也遭延後。<br />\n<br />\n1名在首爾其他公司工作的員工向該報表示，SK海力士工會應該要知足、停止抱怨，三星的特別獎金是月薪5倍，其他公司員工已經感受到很深的相對剝奪感，SK海力士員工獎金比三星還高，但仍不滿足。<br />\n<br />\n對此，SK海力士表示，獎金發放由管理階層決定，並非勞資協議的主題，因為相關協議僅涉及員工的基本薪資和福利等待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2687597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2687597&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1a5fc57d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2687597&h=dcbf4941\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2687597</a>"},{"pid":"876952bc59438157cfd8a8f9f3c8905492d69892","tid":1001884,"uid":41928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"底薪係三叔1/2唔講"},{"pid":"4531c936e990fbea5a7c402f14effa8aeb567192","tid":1001884,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876952bc59438157cfd8a8f9f3c8905492d69892","tid":1001884,"uid":41928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"底薪係三叔1/2唔講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"之前俾開幾多先"},{"pid":"81d17a75216a651fceebefbd2688a661b287b777","tid":1001884,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4531c936e990fbea5a7c402f14effa8aeb567192","tid":1001884,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876952bc59438157cfd8a8f9f3c8905492d69892","tid":1001884,"uid":41928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"底薪係三叔1/2唔講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T14:18:36.000Z","msg":"之前俾開幾多先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"當佢只有三星 1/2 , 12倍獎金已經 cover 到 , 另外仲有5個月相等於 2.5個月三星嘅糧仲想點 ?<br />\n<br />\n不過今年三星派 5倍月薪獎金"},{"pid":"537b7920891d3b6e0e3fdcd4b4808984d9e14e9f","tid":1001884,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"無話貪唔貪   有價值  公司計數搵到錢  多多都比<br />\n<br />\n無價值  一個仙都唔想比  仲想你走"}]}